des:
Malaga Radio is an English Speaking Radio Station Broadcasting in Malaga, Costa del Sol.
The station is a one-stop shop for tourists, The Perfect Vacation station with a summer holiday vibe, 
and supported with Radio On-Demand podcasts for you to listen to at your leisure, with a special focus on towns, attractions, and activities.
